author: cbs8
title: The Priceline Group to Webcast 3rd Quarter 2015 Financial Results on November 9
text:
The Priceline Group
NORWALK, Conn. , Oct. 13, The Priceline Group (Nasdaq: PCLN) announced today that it intends to hold a conference call to discuss its 3rd quarter 2015 financial results on Monday, November 9 at 7:30 a.m. ET . The event will be webcasted live at ir.pricelinegroup.com and the audio will be available for replay on the website for seven days thereafter.
The Priceline Group will post a release containing its 3rd quarter 2015 financial results on the company's Investor Relations website ir.pricelinegroup.com at approximately 7:00 a.m. ET . The release will not be distributed over newswires.
About The Priceline Group
The Priceline Group (NASDAQ: PCLN) is the world leader in online travel and related services, provided to customers and partners in over 200 countries through six primary brands - Booking.com , priceline.com , KAYAK , agoda.com , rentalcars.com , and OpenTable .The Priceline Group's mission is to help people experience the world. For more information, visit PricelineGroup.com .
